WEBVTT

00:00.700 --> 00:04.509
I truly believe that the privilege of a lifetime is being who you are...

00:05.773 --> 00:10.028
...and I just recently embraced that at 51.

00:18.571 --> 00:22.651
I think my strongest power is that at 10 o'clock every Thursday night,...

00:24.331 --> 00:29.093
...I want you to come into my world, I am not gonna come into yours.

00:29.917 --> 00:35.969
You come into my world and you sit with me, my size, my hue, my age,...

00:36.090 --> 00:41.176
...and you, you sit and you experience.

00:41.607 --> 00:46.746
And I think that's the only power I have as an artist, so I thank you for this award.

00:47.132 --> 00:50.711
And I do see her, just like I see me.

